data.description: Spacious  2,206 sq foot, Raised Ranch  located in the Emerald Green lake community. Home features, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths,  hardwood floors, open floor plan, updated kitchen with plenty of cabinets, high efficiency heat pump for heating and cooling. Lower level is completely finished with a laundry area, half bath, a den and a seperate family room with a home theater projector for watching sports games and movies with friends.  Through patio doors is an oversized deck, great for entertaining. There is plenty of storage space both in and out, with 2 storage sheds on the property. The community offers 3 lakes, new heated swiming pools, renovated facilities and an awesome gym. Conviently located to Rt 17, the Resorts  World Catskills Casino, Bethel Performing Arts Center, and all that Sullivan County has to offer.  Only 90 minutes to NYC.
